{"tid":1287132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提醒所有怕被48小時拘留既義士，你地係絕對有權利唔舒服呼吸困難，要求入醫院！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-05T05:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T17:39:18.000Z","uid":222970,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f990dd99562a37f898812d288954941927a1363c","tid":1287132,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:41:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6PscALJtbzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6PscALJtbzU&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=3ad30a2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6PscALJtbzU</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家聽下<br />\n<br />\n另外我唔希望見到有義士被拘留果陣<br />\n呼吸困難 訓係地下 然後休克<br />\n千其唔好身體不適啊！<br />\n到時d警察奈你唔何架啦 又拎唔到你口供<br />\n你係醫院 d警察又做唔到d咩 咁多醫護人員睇住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道大家好想警民合作，但可惜<br />\n我地年輕人體弱多病 要經常出入醫院 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千其唔好扮病！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3c41fd7d78c5c31a0a8880ace9390871036ca9ed","tid":1287132,"uid":35842,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZhmKaF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZhmKaF.png&h=f9298eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGkb6o3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGkb6o3.gif&h=9ad696d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38deefc9b1053b8f212f006224d09e8902809ca0","tid":1287132,"uid":222970,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:43:59.000Z","msg":". 公眾收費- 符合資格人士<br />\n服務\t收費/ 港幣<br />\n急症室\t每次診症180元<br />\n住院費用(急症病床)\t入院費75元，每天120元註1,註2<br />\n住院費用(療養/ 復康、護養及精神科病床)\t每天100元註1,註2<br />\n專科門診(包括專職醫療診所)\t首次診症135元，其後每次診症80元，每種藥物15元註5<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家唔好為左慳180蚊 <br />\n有病一定要立刻入醫院</span></span>"},{"pid":"607a791e69a93ce359fe075ea2d0d6a4116a82f7","tid":1287132,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:46:02.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"aedd3e347c9a4d6957c17c6f1227f39928ac83aa","tid":1287132,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"前排喺香港公園散步 無啦啦好焗好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就成日呼吸困難 喘曬氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家一病發就要留院觀察"},{"pid":"c787358e88a1849d35a48c79fa64cd3c84f4658e","tid":1287132,"uid":222970,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"aedd3e347c9a4d6957c17c6f1227f39928ac83aa","tid":1287132,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"前排喺香港公園散步 無啦啦好焗好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就成日呼吸困難 喘曬氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家一病發就要留院觀察"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:52:52.000Z","msg":"嗱 你唔好亂講 你只係發夢散步<br />\n<br />\n我分享下之前自己經驗<br />\n之前我比幾隻防暴狗捉住 佢地幾個人拉我出黎<br />\n點知我突然病發 呼吸困難 然後佢地就call救護車<br />\n最後冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直情係冇狗跟入黎醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803261729b276feb37c96e14adcb9363c0583476","tid":1287132,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:58:25.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"87de5c72cd68b8dc3336e5a5a9e84210549a2c28","tid":1287132,"uid":220723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"